OL,3,CFamily's tribute to 'perfect son' as
OL,4,Cmurder investigation continues
OL,6,FThe family of Craig Hurcombe have paid
OL,7,Ftribute to a "perfect son" and much-
OL,8,Floved brother and uncle following his
OL,9,Fdeath in January.
OL,11,FThe 39-year-old from Rowde disappeared
OL,12,Fon New Year's Day and was reported
OL,13,Fmissing to police on Saturday 10
OL,14,FJanuary.
OL,16,FA murder investigation was launched
OL,17,Fand human remains, believed to belong
OL,18,Fto Mr Hurcombe, were discovered in
OL,19,FGurney Slade days later.
