OL,3,CFamily's tribute to 'perfect son' as
OL,4,Cmurder investigation continues
OL,6,FMichael Bretton, 40, of Armoury Road,
OL,7,FShaftesbury, Dorset, has been charged
OL,8,Fwith murder and one count of stalking
OL,9,Finvolving fear of violence against a
OL,10,Fwoman and is listed to appear at
OL,11,FBristol Crown Court for trial on
OL,12,FMonday 13 July.
OL,14,FMr Hurcombe's mum, Nicola, and dad,
OL,15,FPaul, have issued a tribute to him on
OL,16,Fbehalf of the family, remembering him
OL,17,Fas a "perfect son" and keen sportsman.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
