OL,3,CFamily's tribute to 'perfect son' as
OL,4,Cmurder investigation continues
OL,6,F"Craig was the perfect son and an
OL,7,Findependent man, and we are living
OL,8,Fwith unimaginable loss and a huge hole
OL,9,Fin our lives which we will never come
OL,10,Fto terms with," they said.
OL,12,F"Craig is survived by eight nieces and
OL,13,Fnephews; Skye, Maddie, Riley, Tillie-
OL,14,FMae, Archie, Harvey, Oakley, and
OL,15,FBrodie, who miss him and cannot
OL,16,Funderstand why he is not there to play
OL,17,Fwith them.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
