OL,3,CFamily's tribute to 'perfect son' as
OL,4,Cmurder investigation continues
OL,6,F"Skye, the eldest niece, has lost her
OL,7,Fbest friend, whom she spent a lot of
OL,8,Ftime eating out and going to watch
OL,9,FBath Rugby with.
OL,11,F"Craig was very hardworking,
OL,12,Fambitious, and very well thought of in
OL,13,Fhis circle of work, especially his
OL,14,Fboss, who has expressed his gratitude
OL,15,Ffor all Craig did for the company.
OL,17,F"Craig has two sisters, Laura and
OL,18,FJessica, and one brother, Ashley, who
OL,19,Fare grieving a brother they love. He
OL,20,Fhad his whole life ahead of him, and
OL,21,Fthat was needlessly taken away.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU
