OL,3,CFamily's tribute to 'perfect son' as
OL,4,Cmurder investigation continues
OL,6,F"Craig was a keen sportsman from the
OL,7,Fage of eleven. He played rugby for
OL,8,FSheldon School, Chippenham Rugby Club
OL,9,Fand Wiltshire and Dorset until the age
OL,10,Fof 18.
OL,12,F"Craig then went on to play for
OL,13,FDevizes Rugby Club, until recently,
OL,14,Fwhere he had a tight network of
OL,15,Ffriends who have been left distraught
OL,16,Fby his death, but have memories of
OL,17,Ftheir trip watching the Lions rugby
OL,18,Ftour in Australia in 2025.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
