OL,6,F"Craig was also vice-president of
OL,7,FDevizes Rugby Club, and many other
OL,8,Fclubs both near and far have left
OL,9,Ftributes to Craig which has made us
OL,10,Faware of how loved he was.
OL,12,F"His meaningless death had an impact
OL,13,Fon so many people, both old and young."
